#
# Purpose (see docs/diagnostics/dgx-spark-uma-memory-freeze.md, "Attempt 13"
# §17, "Attempt 14A" §18, "Attempt 14B" §19):
#
# Attempt 13 (.env.step37-fi-aot-tp2-ep-ray-tuned-kv8g-debug, EP ON + fixed
# --kv-cache-memory-bytes 8589934592, MARLIN NvFp4 MoE backend auto-selected)
